# web/build/ is intentionally committed — the potato is a Le Potato SBC,
# too weak to run pnpm install + vite build in any reasonable time on
# every self-update. Built locally instead; the .githooks/pre-commit
# hook rebuilds it automatically whenever web/src/ changes, so it can't
# drift from source. See gitconfig core.hooksPath and README.
